      • calculateAverageTime

        public static java.util.HashMap<java.lang.String,java.util.ArrayList<UserAppUsage>> calculateAverageTime(java.util.HashMap<java.lang.String,UserAppUsage> list,
                                                                                                         java.util.Date startDate,
                                                                                                         java.util.Date endDate)
        Retrieves the breakdown of users by their usage pattern.

        If a user's total usage time within the query period is less than 1 hr, he is considered a 'mild' user. If the usage time is more than 1 hr but within 5 hrs, he is considered a 'normal user'. Else, he is classified as an 'intense' user.

        Parameters:
        list - the list of users and their app usage times
        startDate - the start date of query period
        endDate - the end date of query period
        Returns:
        the list containing the category type and the respective users
